tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE Students (
    student_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    student_name TEXT,
    enrollment_date DATE,
    graduation_date DATE,
    overall_gpa FLOAT
)
CREATE TABLE students (student_id INT PRIMARY KEY, student_name STRING, grade_level STRING, gender STRING)\n
CREATE TABLE courses (course_id INT PRIMARY KEY, course_name STRING, teacher STRING, grade_level STRING)\n
CREATE TABLE enrollments (enrollment_id INT PRIMARY KEY, student_id INT, course_id INT, enrollment_date DATE)\n
CREATE TABLE grades (grade_id INT PRIMARY KEY, student_id INT, course_id INT, grade DECIMAL)\n
CREATE TABLE reports (report_id INT PRIMARY KEY, student_id INT, report_date DATE, report_content STRING)\n
